---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="About | Zeitdocs"
  description="About Zeitdocs and its documentation governance products for Confluence."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
      <h1>Practical apps for teams that care about documentation control.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Zeitdocs builds governance-oriented apps for Atlassian Confluence. The work is
        focused on visible signals, clearer admin configuration and documentation that
        helps teams make careful decisions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
